==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Memento
<hw>Me*men"to</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Mementos</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L., remember, be mindful,
imper. of <ets>meminisse</ets> to remember. See <er>Mention</er>.]</ety>
<def>A hint, suggestion, token, or memorial, to awaken memory; that
which reminds or recalls to memory; a souvenir.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Seasonable <qex>mementos</qex> may be useful.</q>
<rj><qau>Bacon.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Memento mori</ent>⟦br⟧
\'d8
